{"tid":797295,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"索償案申中止聆訊　壹傳媒勝訴","createTime":"2018-08-28T11:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T13:17:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9a97a124aa376f96a27320af6cd6518c0b9215","tid":797295,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:45:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180828/20486302\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180828%2F20486302&d=y9%2F9aHg93Q5DxJqxdNSMdr5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=fa37b8ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180828%2F20486302&h=e7b8f099\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180828/20486302</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月28日 <br />\n<br />\n索償案申中止聆訊　壹傳媒勝訴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180828/large/a0804a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180828%2Flarge%2Fa0804a.gif&h=f521368e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃浩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】壹傳媒向商人黃浩出售《壹週刊》告吹，遭對方入稟高等法院控告毀約，索償4.4億元。壹傳媒申請中止聆訊，指爭議應交由仲裁庭處理。高院昨判壹傳媒勝訴，下令中止聆訊，等候仲裁結果，並下令黃一方支付懲罰性訟費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃浩須付懲罰性訟費<br />\n<br />\n黃浩於去年8月作價3.2億元，收購港台《壹週刊》業務，並透過旗下Gossip Daily Limited，與壹傳媒旗下公司簽訂買賣協議，其後曾支付8,800萬元保證金。至今年2月，壹傳媒以沒有收到承諾的1.48億元為由，宣佈交易告吹。<br />\n<br />\n不過，黃浩指壹傳媒一方收款出現問題卻中止交易屬毀約，遂興訟追究。另外，黃又指壹傳媒一方誹謗及惡意發佈失實陳述，並用不當手段令其受損，包括指示員工毋須聽從其指令及裁員等。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒一方則指，買賣協議的仲裁條款訂明，任何爭議均須交由仲裁庭處理，故於今年4月入稟香港國際仲裁中心指控黃一方毀約，並在高院申請中止聆訊。黃一方雖同意仲裁庭可處理合約糾紛，但指誹謗等爭拗與合約無關，應繼續在高院處理。<br />\n<br />\n高院暫委法官楊家雄昨頒佈判詞指，買賣協議的用字清晰，表明即使是非合約性質的責任問題，也須交由仲裁庭處理，加上其餘的爭拗與合約糾紛息息相關，若原告在仲裁庭被裁定毀約，其餘指控亦不會成立，故下令中止聆訊，並下令黃一方支付懲罰性訟費。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCA305/18<br />\n■記者梁偉強  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n防登革熱　長洲校園備滅蚊燈迎開學<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n殺妻案重審　貨車司機判囚終身"},{"pid":"b81fa6834a690423f7e5d37293f68dec342790d5","tid":797295,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a89b3d518bf7eaa8ba12b9e2b082af263d2d0f","tid":797295,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:06:18.000Z","msg":"曲線送錢係乜玩法 有乜任務"},{"pid":"ed9ce06572cc0505e568762dcfacfb1b689e5f0f","tid":797295,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c6445e30c3822bf041e50c1e7c598b9ef1a32c3","tid":797295,"uid":202340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a5a89b3d518bf7eaa8ba12b9e2b082af263d2d0f","tid":797295,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:06:18.000Z","msg":"曲線送錢係乜玩法 有乜任務"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:07:42.000Z","msg":"8800萬玩殘肥佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213fbdd1160c890eefbb24fdf5b042c1bc643f6c","tid":797295,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:08:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a3afccd3fc56cb9068ea2bb7ea271513e4d8ba2","tid":797295,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:17:41.000Z","msg":"wrong <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5743ab92c17ef0037dda56b7dd424182a4aa82","tid":797295,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:19:02.000Z","msg":"wrong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a409f993566a62075b6bfa68d3361566c4814996","tid":797295,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c6445